will be with us...

426
00:20:45,458 --> 00:20:46,291
So together--

427
00:20:46,375 --> 00:20:47,791
[CHIDORI]
Not on your life!

428
00:20:47,875 --> 00:20:50,000
[SOUSUKE]
K-Kaname?

429
00:20:50,083 --> 00:20:52,291
[CHIDORI] Why don't the
two of you just go make out

430
00:20:52,375 --> 00:20:53,708
