a special relationship, right?

432
00:20:58,625 --> 00:21:00,000
See ya!

433
00:21:01,958 --> 00:21:03,416
[TESSA]
Sorry to keep you waiting!

434
00:21:03,500 --> 00:21:05,166
Shall we go home now?

435
00:21:06,791 --> 00:21:09,083
[TESSA]
Mr. Sagara?

436
00:21:09,166 --> 00:21:11,708
[SOUSUKE] They left me high
and dry, didn't they?

437
00:21:13,291 --> 00:21:16,416
[TESSA] Hey, what's the matter?
Are you still not feeling well?

438
00:21:16,500 --> 00:21:17,916
----[SOUSUKE] Why?
--You look terrible.

439
00:21:18,000 --> 00:21:19,625
--Why has she pushed me
--You should've taken

