448
00:21:40,125 --> 00:21:42,375
[TESSA] Mr. Sagara!

449
00:21:42,458 --> 00:21:45,625
[SOLDIER] We received word that
Sergeant Sagara's collapsed.

450
00:21:45,708 --> 00:21:46,916
