452
00:21:48,333 --> 00:21:50,750
It was foolish to even
think of entrusting her

453
00:21:50,833 --> 00:21:52,250
to a youngster like that!

454
00:21:52,333 --> 00:21:54,833
Sergeant Sagara is an
inappropriate target

455
00:21:54,916 --> 00:21:55,958
