457
00:21:57,250 --> 00:21:58,583
[SOLDIERS]
Uh... Sir!

458
00:21:58,666 --> 00:22:01,083
[MARDUKAS] Officers,
fraternizing with enlisted men

459
00:22:01,166 --> 00:22:03,125
