the rest of the crew.

460
00:22:03,208 --> 00:22:06,083
[KALININ] Sousuke couldn't
possibly make a move on her.

461
00:22:06,166 --> 00:22:08,083
[MARDUKAS] I believe I will have
to raise a formal objection.

462
00:22:08,166 --> 00:22:09,541
